snippet.title: Baldi's Basics The Ancient Save – What We're Creating for the New Game (Releasing Nov 16)
snippet.description:
In this video, we’re giving you an exclusive first look at Baldi's Basics The Ancient Save, the highly anticipated new game releasing on November 16! Watch as we reveal what we're creating and get ready for the next chapter in the Baldi's Basics series. Don't miss out on all the exciting features we're working on!
